---
title: Loaded Quinoa Bowls with Barbecue Sweet Potatoes, Artichokes, Feta Cheese, and Croutons
description: Hot potato alert! The sweet potatoes in this recipe are about as gloriously tender, crisp, and steamy as can be thanks to a shallow frying technique. Plus, they’re seasoned with smoky spices,— basically, a riff on barbecue sweet potato chips. They’re not the only good thing about this recipe, either: artichokes, quinoa, baguette croutons, feta, and tomatoes ensure that things stay filling and fully loaded
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/loaded-quinoa-bowls-34b5376d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/loaded-quinoa-bowls-5addf1ecae08b54fc11b20d2-0e7d10fa.pdf
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
